              <text>Definition of <emphasis style="bold">Residual Claims levy</emphasis> in section 59(1): repeal.</text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 59(1): add:</text>
              <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                <def-para id="DLM2417619" quote="1">
                  <para quote="1">
                    <text><def-term id="DLM2417620">Work Account levy</def-term> means the levy payable under section 168, 168A, 168B, or 211 of the applicable Act</text>
                  </para>
                </def-para>
              </amend>
              <follow-text space-before="no">.</follow-text>
            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Section 59(3): omit <amend.in quote="1">Residual Claims levy</amend.in> in each place where it appears and substitute in each case <amend.in quote="1">Work Account levy</amend.in>.</text>
